      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, i do sit with it. but it's not like a peaceful meditation or anything. it's just this constant realization that no matter what i do, nothing actually changes. i'm just moving parts around in a void. if everything is just destined to decay and fall apart anyway, why bother staying in the middle of it?",
